Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次回到數碼世界的太一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在餐廳裏找到了被迫留下來工作的大和與阿丈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大和與阿丈重修舊好的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和的徽章發出了光芒 加魯魯獸進化成為完全體的獸人加魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 當時的光子郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十四話「擊破 超比多獸!」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 休息一下好不好 我已經好累了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都要找到玄內老人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們已經找了兩個多月了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管花幾個月的時間 我都要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不走 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…光子郎 等等我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又要挨吸血魔獸大王的罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會被吸血魔獸大王罵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惡魔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底什麼時候才能把那些孩子們的徽章搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很、很快就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎麼相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請相信我的眼睛 吸血魔獸大王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果你辦不到 那你可要有心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次再搶不到手的話 大王一定會殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道、我知道我一定會沒命的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 是被選召的孩子之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要能夠找到玄內老人 那麼一定就可以知道徽章的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最欣賞光子郎的一點 就是你什麼事情都要追根究底的求知慾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說嘛 我會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有別的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過玄內老人他到底在什麼地方呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有指示牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有生猛大便掉落 請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思呀? 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 我們從這一邊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼這樣 這邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有無底大便池 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 我們走這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生猛大便 請留心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大便…大便…大便…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶到處都是大便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功 成功 大勝利了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲獸 你不能飛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 飛上去結果又會掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要掉到什麼地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地獄 怎、怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了! 我才不要去地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受自己慾望操控的人都會掉到地獄去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我覺得我們並沒有被自己的慾望牽著鼻子走呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:06:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們有 就是你追根究底的求知慾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我不可以想要知道所有的事情嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個想知道為什麼的求知慾會讓你掉講地獄 永遠也出不來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你又有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好奇求知的慾望越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要掉進地獄裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不要下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們就放棄凡事都想知道的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我最欣賞的就是光子郎的求知慾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去 我們兩個都會掉到地獄裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能夠丟掉求知慾?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想知道 我不想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是什麼地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是神聖又神秘的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是職司神聖又神秘的宇宙的宇宙腦魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙腦魔 身份不明 全身充滿詭異氣氛的數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕招「惡魔烈焰紅唇」讓對手品嚐屈辱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你剛剛丟掉的求知慾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓它污染神聖而又神秘的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我把它處理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是讓宇宙能量充滿你的全身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙能量如何充滿全身」的課本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙能量的基本就在於呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎你在說什麼 我怎麼都聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確的呼吸法是由右胸發出阿爾法波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要念了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 血液循環變好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的全身將充滿力量 因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 你到哪裏去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家了 回到現實世界了 滾球獸它也跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 那你是不是不回來這裏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那你再跟我聯絡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一那邊好像很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有這一股宇宙能量是一切追求安逸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求知之心在不求知之心的隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有人丟掉求知慾 當然也會有人想買一顆求知之心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就是宇宙裏販賣「心」的人 宇宙腦魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快招呼客人來買吧 生意一定會變好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請、請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店商品樣式齊全 絕對滿足每位顧客不同的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看過這個孩子和這只數碼寶貝?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 有…有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 請您稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是那個孩子的求知慾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 難道你是來鬧場的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是這個孩子手裏的這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們這裏是「心」的專賣店 不賣這一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 我這裏有好多新鮮的大便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇! 大便…大便…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你願意跟我以物換物嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意 我願意!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對設法弄到手 好跟你交換新鮮的大便 你等著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A、B、C
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D、E、F
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G、H…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在學習怎麼樣讓宇宙能量充滿全身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要吵我 討厭!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I、J、K
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L、M、N…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事我忘了告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙腦魔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習宇宙能量之前 你必須把一切身外之物丟掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 所有的身外之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 不能丟呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把徽章還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續學習宇宙能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O、P、Q
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R、S、T
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U、V、W
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X、Y…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個這個 快點拿給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 一手交錢一手交貨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有好大便嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我現在馬上就拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要耍我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混球!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E、F、G
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H、I、J
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K、L…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫 泡沫 泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了! 不是叫你不要打擾我學習的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫…泡沫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫…泡沫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠找到玄內老人 一定就可以知道徽章的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最欣賞光子郎的一點 就是你什麼事情都要追根究底的求知慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫…泡沫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫 泡沫 泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是我害你退化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫 泡沫 泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙腦魔 不要這麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我覺得你很煩哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等、等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要騙我了 回去 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果我不帶那個徽章回去 不知道吸血魔獸大王會怎樣處置我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼! 那是你家的事 我可管不了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你幫個忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實在很煩啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我丟掉的徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有求知慾 什麼事情都不明白 怎麼會這樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有一種受騙上當的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫 泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快去把丟掉的徽章與求知之心拿回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你回去 你是聽不懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 泡沫獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑!把徽章還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的徽章終於又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸 都是你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫 泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門哪! 開門哪!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門 快開門!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我丟掉的求知之心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個什麼也不想知道的人 那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡學習一切不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫 泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寶貴的求知之心 把你丟了真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道 我要弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 不要碰那個求知之心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡沫獸 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟲獸進化…比多獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔烈焰紅唇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比多獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我宇宙腦魔 不然你就要倒霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比多獸 站起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比多獸超進化…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超比多獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超比多獸 由比多獸超講化而成的昆蟲型數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕招是用巨大的頭角刺撞敵人的「超大角炮」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔烈焰紅唇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超比多獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣? 知道我的厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎…光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能量輸出太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 阿岳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨角獸 巴達獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕獸 你給光子郎抱看 好像小嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子郎 趕快放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 你太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選召的孩子們哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄內老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個扭曲的世界還沒有修正回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你們前面要走的路 我為你們準備了這個世界的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「數碼寶貝大百科」 你們可以作為參考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數碼寶貝大百科
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 超比多獸 昆蟲型的數碼寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫我耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血魔獸大王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們的徽章呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 準備受罰吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊! 吸血魔獸大王 饒了我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美在一大群怪蛙獸的伺候之下變得更任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但讓太一進了監牢 還跟巴魯獸吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是絕對不能放棄 當徽章發出光芒 美美真心唱歌喚醒了怪蛙皇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒有想到它是個暴君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回數碼寶貝大冒險\N「沉睡的暴君 怪蛙皇!」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 冒險越來越深入了

